2. about ERC-404

ERC-404 is an experimental token standard on the Ethereum blockchain that combines the characteristics of fungible tokens (ERC-20) and non-fungible tokens (ERC-721). It enables fractional ownership of NFTs, allowing multiple users to hold shares in a single NFT.
